    "body": "``` rust\nextern crate sync;\nuse sync::mutex::Mutex;\n\nstruct Node {\n   mutex : Mutex\n}\nstruct Link {\n   to : &Node,\n   from : &Node,\n}\n\nfn deadlock(link : &mut Link) {\n  let to_guard = link.to.mutex.lock();\n  let from_guard = link.from.mutex.lock();   // Deadlock can occur here\n  drop(to_guard);\n  drop(from_guard);\n}\n```\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
