    "body": "The simplest solution to the problem you gave is to just lock the mutexes in address order.  You could write a series of functions or methods on tuples of mutexes to do this.  Example for pairs: http://is.gd/aNnVl5\n\nThis of course requires the order to be followed everywhere in the code, which can be difficult to verify.\n",
